Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.24,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:18.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:26.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:33.55,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:36.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:40.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:44.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:48.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:59.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:02.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:15.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:18.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:24.87,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs195\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,180.389)}Defeat It
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:24.87,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,690.389)}Double Riders!! Siomaneking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.71,0:01:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get a bite, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pulling! It's pulling hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:01:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a big one, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor. Give it your best, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan's great oceanographer,\NProfessor Sakai,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't much of a fisherman, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better catch something\Nto impress your wife and son!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it, Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Sakai...\NI have business with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, you will come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Katsuura region is also\Nknown as Kii no Matsushima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsurushima, Kameshima...\NThere are all kinds of islands around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And the valleys are all\Nbubbling up with hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nachi Falls is very popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To your right, you can see the open sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea is vast and large...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful area, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the famous Pacific\NOcean. It's quite large, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a great view?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels great to be freed\Nfrom the world of asphalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to take things easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's that boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. That boat there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a fishing boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's on board...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it was set adrift?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But to have nobody on board...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a strange boat there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we stop a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a strange boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A strange boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not cooperate already, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought you'd long had a dream\Nto build cities on the ocean floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,ranching fish and farming seaweed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The real issue is who was\Non that fishing boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The oceanographer Professor\NSakai and his assistants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,His wife and child are\Nstaying in the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Professor Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Masao's dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Masao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I met him in the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think they heard\Nabout what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not in the hotel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They went to see the whale museum in Taiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki's searching for them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:40.61,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\c&H1C3C49&}Whale Museum
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, aren't they big?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They certainly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, let's go to the aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, there's fish swimming everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we're at the bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that one's called.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's sharks, too! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Masao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I just saw a scary monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dolphins are smart, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Your father said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to train dolphins\Nto guard the fish ranches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, I'm going to get\Nan aqualung and become a sea cowboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Masao, hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Masao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Masao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking you to meet Professor Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker... where\Nhave you taken the Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! I'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Siomaneking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gladly, Siomaneking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, take them to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A formidable opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Impressed by my power, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you... this isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:33.98,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea why Shocker\Nmight be after Professor Sakai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband's passion project\Nwas the creation of underwater cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Underwater cities?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just what he told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was an underwater\Nranch for cultivating fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and an underwater farm\Nfor raising seaweed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And what was the other thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Underwater oil fields and mines!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! It was an underwater\Ncity built around those things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Very impressive! Absolutely brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, that's what Shocker's after, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're planning to\Nbuild an underwater city.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to foil their plan\Nand rescue the professor ASAP...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But where could their base possibly be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the big question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Papa is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Masao! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere left for you to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Masao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Masao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Masao!\N- Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Masao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could Masao and his mother have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of Taki, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! Look! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... this is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pursue. You call Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That damned Rider is on his way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape me, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come, Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:16:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiko! Masao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Professor Sakai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel like working with us yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You cowards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker will do anything\Nto achieve its goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Will you help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You stubborn fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed, Siomaneking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Masao! Masao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Professor Sakai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Masao! Masao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you first. Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown yourself, Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But your coming was predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't struggle, or I'll throw you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't survive a fall\Ninto the ocean from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Get the doctor to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We can finish off both Riders at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you gone, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:23.90,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:26.90,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:30.99,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:34.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:38.12,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:41.75,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:44.38,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:48.78,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:52.64,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:55.97,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:06.48,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:09.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:13.99,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:17.54,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:21.17,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:24.50,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:27.51,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:31.09,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:35.74,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:39.27,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Double Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe here. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:55.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The duel between the two Riders\Nand Shocker in the southern Kii Peninsula
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:57.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,ended with the Riders triumphant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.76,0:23:00.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Summer tranquility returns\Nto the Kumano-nada Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.47,0:23:04.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but Shocker will surely attack Japan again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.06,0:23:06.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We'll be counting on you then, our Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:10.68,Cont,,0,65,156,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:13.80,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(290.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:15.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As blood banks are attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:18.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the sound of someone licking\Ntheir lips can be heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:22.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Blood-sucking monster Shiraculas\Ngets its hands around Rider's neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:26.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next time: "The Deadly Blood-Sucker!!\NGive It Your All, Rider Kid Corps."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:27.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let us watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:30.82,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,140.389)}The Deadly Blood-Sucker!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:30.82,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,710.389)}Give It Your All, Rider Kid Corps
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:50.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:57.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:24:01.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:05.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:08.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.92,0:24:12.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat It, Double Riders!!\NSiomaneking
Comment: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Deadly Blood-Sucker!!\NGive It Your All, Rider Kid Corps